title: RHODubai: The Girl and the Goat
description:
This week on The Real Housewives of Dubai, the women celebrate American Thanksgiving, and no - Caroline Stanbury is not forced to wear a turkey hat again. However, Ayan does present an unexpected gift to Lesa.

Watch this recap with Crappens on Demand here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/67603714
